1
00:00:51,479 --> 00:00:51,960
Master.

2
00:00:54,439 --> 00:00:54,799
Master.

3
00:00:55,320 --> 00:00:55,840
Master, wake up.

4
00:01:01,359 --> 00:01:02,640
You're meeting Li Qiankun today.

5
00:01:09,920 --> 00:01:10,359
Elder Li.

6
00:01:10,760 --> 00:01:13,560
How are your documents coming along?

7
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:18,280
Feifan, you know we're no ordinary company.

8
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:20,640
We have so many projects.

9
00:01:21,959 --> 00:01:23,079
It takes time to sort them out.

10
00:01:25,959 --> 00:01:26,719
Right, Xiaoyue?

11
00:01:28,159 --> 00:01:28,680
Yes.

12
00:01:29,359 --> 00:01:30,280
What are you standing there for?

13
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:31,519
Pour Feifan some tea.

14
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:32,920
No need.

15
00:01:42,079 --> 00:01:42,519
Elder Li.

16
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,040
Lately my backer

17
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:45,560
threw a huge fit at me.

18
00:01:45,959 --> 00:01:47,079
Said I wasn't getting things done.

19
00:01:47,599 --> 00:01:49,799
So regarding the timeline for this,

20
00:01:50,239 --> 00:01:52,040
I can't wait around for you much longer.

21
00:01:57,079 --> 00:01:57,599
Seven days.

22
00:01:58,079 --> 00:01:59,480
I'll give you seven more days.

23
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:01,920
We'll sign the contract in seven days, okay?

24
00:02:02,359 --> 00:02:02,879
Feifan.

25
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:03,719
Elder Li.

26
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,439
I have things to attend to at the hospital.

27
00:02:05,799 --> 00:02:06,560
I have to go now.

28
00:02:07,359 --> 00:02:09,000
Feifan, hear me out.

29
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:10,319
You know

30
00:02:10,879 --> 00:02:13,159
our Xiaoyue has always been clever.

31
00:02:13,319 --> 00:02:15,560
A grown man like you out here needs looking after.

32
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:19,120
Why not let Xiaoyue take care of you for a few days?

33
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:21,680
She's very sensible.

34
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:27,199
Elder Li, I'll take my leave.

35
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,800
What are you waiting for? Go!

36
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,439
Dad, I found out.

37
00:02:44,159 --> 00:02:46,039
Li Qiankun recently met with Ren Feifan.

38
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,759
Ren Feifan.

39
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:50,960
Did you find out what they discussed?

40
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:55,960
Li Qiankun's been chasing exclusive government deals.

41
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:57,919
Ren Feifan's side is still unclear.

42
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:00,960
Good.

43
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,000
Keep digging.

44
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,719
No matter what,

45
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:09,560
Li Qiankun must not touch the museum project.

46
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:10,960
Got it.

47
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:11,520
Also,

48
00:03:12,319 --> 00:03:13,840
put the word out to all our contacts.

49
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:18,159
Any other exclusive government projects he goes for,

50
00:03:18,919 --> 00:03:21,039
make sure none of them succeed.

51
00:03:22,439 --> 00:03:23,039
Understood.

52
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:27,960
They won't let me touch a thing?

53
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,599
They're trying to cut off my livelihood!

54
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:35,159
Go.

55
00:03:36,639 --> 00:03:37,520
Go prepare the stuff.

56
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,639
Wh-what stuff?

57
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:40,599
Evidence.

58
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,039
Evidence of what?

59
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:44,800
All the dirty deeds the Wangs have done over the years.

60
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,719
Didn't I tell you to keep records?

61
00:03:47,639 --> 00:03:48,360
Yes, yes, yes.

62
00:03:48,479 --> 00:03:49,360
I've kept it all.

63
00:03:49,919 --> 00:03:50,560
I'll go get it for you.

64
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:02,280
Hello.

65
00:04:03,599 --> 00:04:04,599
The word's been put out.

66
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:05,919
Just wait for the good news.

67
00:04:09,759 --> 00:04:10,159
Dad.

68
00:04:10,919 --> 00:04:11,400
Look at this.

69
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:12,400
It's the Wanli Pill.

70
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:15,120
The Lis want the rights to sell Wanli Pills.

71
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:20,240
He wouldn't lift a finger without a payoff.

72
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:22,920
Old man Li's ambition is huge.

73
00:04:23,519 --> 00:04:26,000
Wanli Pills have proven themselves in the south.

74
00:04:26,759 --> 00:04:27,519
Once they launch,

75
00:04:28,839 --> 00:04:30,000
there'll be no competition.

76
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:33,959
The Lis want the entire northern market.

77
00:04:36,439 --> 00:04:38,319
Mr. Wang, Mr. Li had this sent over.

78
00:04:54,319 --> 00:04:55,639
That old bastard.

79
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,439
I wasn't planning to wipe him out.

80
00:04:58,040 --> 00:05:00,199
But he had the nerve to threaten me.

81
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:03,920
Since he wants to crush the Wang family,

82
00:05:04,959 --> 00:05:07,759
then the Li family no longer needs to exist.

83
00:05:17,199 --> 00:05:18,000
Chengren.

84
00:05:18,399 --> 00:05:20,720
Did you receive what I sent you?

85
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:22,399
Yes, I got it.

86
00:05:23,319 --> 00:05:27,040
So, is it enough to trade for the project?

87
00:05:27,639 --> 00:05:29,600
More than enough.

88
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:32,560
The project is yours.

89
00:05:32,959 --> 00:05:33,639
Elder Li.

90
00:05:42,199 --> 00:05:44,000
Feifan, a pleasure doing business with you.

91
00:05:44,519 --> 00:05:45,240
Likewise.

92
00:05:52,839 --> 00:05:55,319
Feifan, Xiaoyue's quite something, isn't she?

93
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:57,360
When you have time,

94
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:59,480
bring her to meet your backer.

95
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,000
There'll be a chance.

96
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:07,680
So when do we sign the contract?

97
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:13,000
I heard the Pharmaceutical Association is holding

98
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:14,800
a development summit for Beishi pharma companies tomorrow.

99
00:06:15,959 --> 00:06:18,720
Announcing it there would be perfect.

100
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,319
It'll give us more publicity too.

101
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,959
Excellent. Very good.

102
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,560
You're truly a promising young man.

103
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:28,600
Not like that good-for-nothing in my family.

104
00:06:28,839 --> 00:06:30,879
Let's stay in close contact from now on.

105
00:06:31,279 --> 00:06:32,920
I'll help you along when I can.

106
00:06:34,399 --> 00:06:35,519
Then I'll head back to prepare.

107
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:39,600
I'll see you out. Grandpa.

108
00:06:53,319 --> 00:06:55,800
Everyone, halfway through this meeting,

109
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:57,800
we have some good news to announce.

110
00:06:58,560 --> 00:07:00,079
Our Li Group,

111
00:07:00,199 --> 00:07:01,959
led by Elder Li Qiankun,

112
00:07:02,839 --> 00:07:04,120
has officially secured...

113
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:04,720
Hold on.

114
00:07:07,519 --> 00:07:08,160
Everyone,

115
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:13,040
I also have some news about the Li Group.

116
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:17,680
I'm sure you'll find it interesting.

117
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:22,120
The Li Group, at its cultivation bases,

118
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:25,839
has been mass-growing banned herbs like Aconite

119
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:26,959
and Pinellia Rhizome.

120
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:29,560
Their workers, due to growing these herbs,

121
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:31,759
have suffered fatal incidents.

122
00:07:35,519 --> 00:07:37,199
The Wangs and Lis are partners.

123
00:07:37,879 --> 00:07:39,959
Elder Li worked so hard on this project.

124
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:42,680
Young Mr. Wang, what are you stirring up here?

125
00:07:44,839 --> 00:07:47,439
You brat, you want to bring us all down, huh?

126
00:07:48,839 --> 00:07:50,000
I've got plenty of evidence.

127
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:52,560
Look.

128
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:54,600
The Wang family told us to grow those herbs.

129
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:57,240
They can't escape blame either.

130
00:07:57,759 --> 00:08:00,079
Here's the cultivation contract we signed with them.

131
00:08:00,079 --> 00:08:00,680
See for yourself.

132
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:02,720
Young Mr. Wang,

133
00:08:03,439 --> 00:08:05,319
the Wangs and Lis are close as family.

134
00:08:05,959 --> 00:08:09,079
Why hurt your allies and please your enemies

135
00:08:10,079 --> 00:08:11,519
by ruining the Li family's deal?

136
00:08:11,519 --> 00:08:13,319
Don't you dare make false accusations.

137
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:15,399
The Wang family didn't sign this.

138
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:19,360
Are you saying our signatures on it are fake?

139
00:08:20,839 --> 00:08:21,720
Of course they're fake.

140
00:08:27,879 --> 00:08:29,360
Our family's signature

141
00:08:30,279 --> 00:08:33,279
changes color under ultraviolet light.

142
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,480
But yours doesn't.

143
00:08:38,759 --> 00:08:40,399
If you don't believe me, let me demonstrate.

144
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:45,720
This is the Li family's contract.

145
00:08:54,639 --> 00:08:56,600
And this one is ours.

146
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:02,840
You...

147
00:09:07,679 --> 00:09:08,960
Wang Wenhao, you set up Elder Li!

148
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:11,080
But as everyone knows,

149
00:09:11,399 --> 00:09:14,000
Wang Pharma has long purchased herbs from the Lis.

150
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,759
That's a fact.

151
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:16,840
That's right.

152
00:09:17,919 --> 00:09:20,399
You passed off Platycodon Root as American Ginseng,

153
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:22,519
and Mulberry Twig for Astragalus Root.

154
00:09:25,039 --> 00:09:25,879
Where's the evidence?

155
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:29,600
Not another fake contract, Elder Li?

156
00:09:32,519 --> 00:09:33,120
Everyone,

157
00:09:33,799 --> 00:09:36,960
the Lis pass off inferior herbs as premium ones,

158
00:09:37,159 --> 00:09:39,080
cut corners in processing,

159
00:09:39,279 --> 00:09:43,200
and resort to anything, from dyeing to sulfur fumigation.

160
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:47,879
Here's all the evidence.

161
00:09:51,679 --> 00:09:52,360
This...

162
00:09:58,679 --> 00:09:59,399
The Li family...

163
00:10:00,039 --> 00:10:00,960
It's over.

164
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:25,039
Looks like your Snipe and Clam Plan didn't work out.

165
00:10:27,399 --> 00:10:29,000
At least it got the Li family back for you.

166
00:10:30,159 --> 00:10:31,559
And cut off one of the Wang family's hands.

167
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:36,080
How's Li Qiankun doing now?

168
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:39,879
This afternoon,

169
00:10:41,639 --> 00:10:43,240
the investigation team is coming to take him away.

170
00:10:57,679 --> 00:10:59,279
Feifan, you're here.

171
00:10:59,759 --> 00:11:00,639
I'm begging you.

172
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:02,600
We still need to work together.

173
00:11:03,279 --> 00:11:04,720
Once I recover, I'll help you along.

174
00:11:05,039 --> 00:11:07,480
I still need to conquer the entire northern market.

175
00:11:07,879 --> 00:11:08,559
Li Qiankun.

176
00:11:09,519 --> 00:11:11,759
Didn't Master Zhang beg you like this back then?

177
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:14,200
Did you spare him?

178
00:11:14,639 --> 00:11:15,039
You...
